<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>F#</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.D#m         G#m
 Qutqarýshym, ǵajapsyń,
.A#           D#m
 Men úshin Sen kóterdiń.
.         G#m
 Eń aýyryn azaptyń,
.C#7          F#     D#m
 Seni dos dep ótermin.

[C1]
.     D#m          G#m
   //  Esimde tógilgen qanyń,
.  C#7           F#
   Qoldaryń jara basqany.
.  D#m            G#m
    Kelip Táńirge men taǵy,
.  A#      A#sus  D#m/D#7
    Bas ıip alǵys aıtamyn. //

[V2]
 Aıtqan Sóziń esimde:
 «Keshir Áke olardy».
 Kez bolǵanyń esimde,
 O, Isa, maǵan jolda.

[V3]
 Shaqyrmasań Sen meni,
 Tartpasań jyly sózbenen
 Júrer edim adasyp,
 Ár qıly jalǵan jolmen.

[V4]
 Másih meni súıgende,
 Ómirime endi nur.
 Tek Isada tynyshtyq,
 Shattyq, ómir maqsatym.</lyrics>
<title>Qutqarýshym, ǵajapsyń ҮРәж124</title>
<author>Neızvesten</author>
<hymn_number>124</hymn_number>
</song>